                    </tgroup>
                </table>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Benefit of the service upgrade kit is to increase clutch tooth engagement that improves
                            shift feel. To optimize this service upgrade kit, it is recommended to thoroughly inspect
                            the 6/7 synchronizer and mating clutch hub for wear and contamination. If there is evidence
                            of this, or even questionable, replace the parts with new product. Failure to do this could
                            affect the operation of the service upgrade kit installed.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
